Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:36.47,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrounded by Zentradi forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:40.15,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,the Macross launches a desperate\NDaedalus Attack on Britai's ship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:44.55,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,which allows an invasion force\Nto stream in from the bow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:47.99,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,turning the city within the ship's\Ninterior into a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:51.29,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(97,141)}DROP OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:19.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:33.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, men!\NCrush them with one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it's anything goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you men doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:47.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay's in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:50.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Minmay"? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:53.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He said Minmay's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:56.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three were telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna meet Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:00.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:06.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:10.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can't damage this\Nplace any longer, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:16.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you men too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:18.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:20.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why are you running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive us, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:27.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't understand how\Nwonderful this place is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:32.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what your reasons are,\Ndesertion is unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:35.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do to you what I did\Nto that other guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:36.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:43.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! You're no longer part of my Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll execute you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:01.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, this is strange!\NThe intruders' ranks are in disarray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:02.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:06.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our chance. Send in our reserve\Nair-defense Valkyrie teams!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:08.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:12.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Brown, Green, and Indigo Squadrons,\Nhead for the ship's bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Engage the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:47.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a movie, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:52.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull Leader, come in!\NLieutenant Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Captain Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:59.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, Captain Hayase"?!\NWhat's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:04.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please send a rescue party\Nto the open-air theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:06.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The open-air theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kaifun all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, who's hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Ichijo!\NLieutenant Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaifun, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:38.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A Minmay doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what it's like!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:18.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:23.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... It's ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:36.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We... all of us... did this,\Nto the doll and to this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Desertion in the face of the enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:51.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the enemy's true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, the legends...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:56.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying we should have heeded them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:03.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's too late! Abort the mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:07.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Temporarily confine the deserters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And what shall we do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:13.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave that to you. Do what you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can investigate the power of\Nthis "culture" if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:18.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:24.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Culture..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:37.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The deserters will only be temporarily confined?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:41.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we allow this, who knows what else will happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:51.21,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! The second I get through\Nfighting, they call me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:54.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,First Lieutenant Ichijo, reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You three!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:02.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm yourself, Lieutenant. They're under armed guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're prisoners, like you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:12.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about?\NWhy are you even here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:16.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, may I explain to the lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:17.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:22.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Ichijo, these men and twenty-three\Nothers wish to defect to our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:24.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Defect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:28.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get serious! We've been fighting these people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:31.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now some of them waltz up and\Nsay they want to defect,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:35.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're supposed to say, "Sure, come\Non in?!" Well, I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:39.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it three to two, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:41.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:45.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Ichijo, I thought\Nyou would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:51.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't take in these defectors,\Nthey'll have nowhere else to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:55.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm just a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:59.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're asking your opinion as someone who's\Nhad direct contact with the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:08.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, please let me have\Na few words with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:15.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we want to live here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:16.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You have culture here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And Minmay's songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:25.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But how do you know this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:28.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We sneaked aboard this ship\Nonce before, as spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:35.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But when we went back,\Nthere was something missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:44.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"These poor beings have only known war."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:50.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, but aren't these sort of\Nweak reasons to desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:53.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's also because you're Protoculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:59.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Protoculture? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still playing dumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with all the power you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:09.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This would seem to support Hayase's theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:13.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, you're seriously asking\Nus to believe her report?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:16.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, we have to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Ichijo, what's your opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:27.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would\Nbe all right to accept them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it two to three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:36.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant, you just said we shouldn't\Naccept them, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:43.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Why should we listen to\Nthe opinion of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:45.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,who can't even explain his reasoning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:52.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,First Lieutenant Ichijo, may I ask\Nwhy you changed your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:57.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. As I reported before, these\Naliens have known only war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:11:00.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that when they came aboard the\NMacross and experienced our culture
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:05.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and how we live our lives, it must have\Nbeen a huge shock for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:08.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we were really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:13.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We were amazed by Minmay's singing,\Nand that men and women lived together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:16.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And that some of you even oppose war!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:20.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,As we got used to it, we started to\Nenjoy living here more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:27.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If what they said is true and they really are in\Nawe of how we live aboard the Macross...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:35.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't quite know how to put it, but maybe\Nwe could forge a friendship with the aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:38.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's an overly optimistic view!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:42.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying we should live\Nwith these aliens?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:45.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They may look like us, but don't go\Nsaying that we're the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:48.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But being aboard the Macross,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:51.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,they've seen for the first time a way\Nof life that isn't just about war!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:53.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we throw them out now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:56.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The emotional argument this time, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:58.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:11:59.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:05.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,As 1st Lt. Ichijo said, the Zentradi forces are\Ncomprised solely of military organizations;
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,they know nothing besides war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:11.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They fight because it's all they know how to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:16.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,For them, the only way to end a war\Nis to annihilate their enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:18.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why we must reject these\Ndefectors and take strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:23.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's why we have to teach them\Nabout things other than war!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:25.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not everything is about victory or defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:28.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we make them see that there's\Nanother way to live their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:31.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'll have opened up the\Navenue to ending this war!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:38.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for a moving speech,\Nbut may I remind you that these are aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:41.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you plan on integrating them\Ninto our civilian population?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:45.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We're in the middle of\Nan important meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:50.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I asked him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Do you have the results?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:55.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:10.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:13.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We had their blood analyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:26.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:31.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Their blood types and genetic makeup\Nare the same as ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought that would be the case,\Nbut to actually be proven right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:43.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So we really could live together,\Ncouldn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're Protoculture, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:51.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we no longer have a reason\Nto treat them as aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:55.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be regarded as normal defectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:02.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, we will accept them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:05.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:13.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can a decision this important really\Nbe made by the Macross alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We should ask High Command for orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of line, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:24.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not feeling well, sir, so if you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.30,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Maistroff...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:37.10,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:42.11,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, we must accept these\Nbizarre circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:52.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I came to see this. It's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:56.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look this bad on the monitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not quite so damaged over here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:04.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I always seem to end up coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:10.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle! Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,, {\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:18.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:22.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Well, Kaifun and Minmay\Nhaven't come back yet, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're at the general hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:27.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The hospital?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kaifun was the only one hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:35.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not serious. Minmay just\Nwanted to stay with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:39.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear! We shouldn't be wasting time here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:44.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but we can't just leave the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:46.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:48.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll watch it while you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You'd do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:52.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Oh! Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:53.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:54.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:11.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:12.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:19.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, I'll make us some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:35.15,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:06.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:07.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:10.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:14.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, it's the civilians, the ones who\Nhave nothing to do with this war...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:17.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,the ones who looked so powerless\Nin the face of war,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:21.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,who could be the key to ending the conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:27.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, don't you want to go\Nto the hospital, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just admit it. You're worried\Nabout Kaifun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I really was concerned about him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:41.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but in all this uproar over the defectors,\NI completely forgot about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:43.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:47.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,this is all because he looks like\Nsomeone I was once in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:57.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But he hates me because I'm a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:18:01.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I even started to doubt the military's\Nway of doing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:05.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Finding someone so opposed to war\Nwas such a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:10.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably like what those defectors felt\Nwhen they found out about our peaceful lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:19.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized that their arrival may have given\Nus a way to end this war, I suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,just lost interest in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:23.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:28.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that strange of me?\NAnyway, Kaifun has his parents
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:31.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and Minmay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you even told her how you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:40.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:57.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't expect her to know how\Nyou feel if you don't tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:01.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want Kaifun to take her away from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:04.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't tell her, you'll regret it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:10.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't mean to\Nlecture you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:12.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see you, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Ichijo, you go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find someone to watch the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:44.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull Squadron, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:53.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Spartan Company, stand by at blocks 4 and 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:57.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirkland Company, move to\Ndefend the Prometheus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:20:00.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, hurry up and switch with me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:02.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:05.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I got caught up in traffic.\NWhat are we up against?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:09.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A small force. I think they\Ncould be stragglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were they hiding all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:15.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We may have finally found the answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but now we have to fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:22.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:26.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are polite today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:34.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:38.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:05.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:07.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your six!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:27.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:32.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Capt. Hayase, please don't tell me we have any\Nmore small forces like this headed for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:34.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:36.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How long is this going to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:40.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can say? War is the only thing\Nour enemies know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:42.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll have to put an end to this someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:48.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:51.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to end it as soon as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:02.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:06.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to go to\NHigh Command!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:10.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain the situation\Nregarding our defectors!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:12.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain? That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.27,0:22:16.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my absolute best to\Nmake them understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:18.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I may even be able to rely\Non my father for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:22.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can do this without\Ntaking those three along?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:27.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll go alone first, then send for\Nthem once I've explained things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:30.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just take them along with me,\Nwho knows what could happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:32.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:34.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:36.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:49.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, I will leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:53.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ready a shuttle at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:56.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You may leave when ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:23:00.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll prepare to leave at once.
