Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:40.35,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa's shuttle heads for Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:43.71,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,where she will plead her case to the heads\Nof the UN Forces High Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:49.15,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,But once separated from the Macross, the\Nshuttle is attacked by Kamujin's forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.25,0:23:53.74,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru and Max race out in their\NValkyries to rescue her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.21,0:23:58.11,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:24:00.17,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"GOODBYE GIRL"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:18.83,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:24.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,A thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:30.15,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:36.94,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The Light struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:42.16,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:48.65,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:52.91,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,And fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:58.06,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\NAs the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.33,0:01:01.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:06.59,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:12.83,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:17.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.14,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.56,0:24:23.22,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.35,0:24:29.75,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.93,0:24:36.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.53,0:24:44.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.31,0:24:50.68,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.04,0:24:56.60,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.88,0:25:04.15,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.42,0:25:15.66,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:01.81,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(87,149)}GOODBYE GIRL
